[[File:Galaxies_Opera_House_Posters.jpg|thumb|300px|Signs for ''The Gungan King'' and other shows outside the Galaxies Opera House]]
'''''The Gungan King''''' was a musical playing at the [[Galaxies Opera House/Legends|Galaxies Opera House]] in [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]. A sign advertising the show was displayed outside of the [[Opera/Legends|opera]] house during a performance of [[Squid Lake/Legends|''Squid Lake'']] attended by [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]]. The sign depicted a stylized illustration of the [[Gungan/Legends|Gungan]] [[Boss/Legends|Boss]] [[Rugor Nass/Legends|Rugor Nass]].<ref name="Revenge of the Clone Menace">''[[Tag & Bink: Revenge of the Clone Menace]]''</ref>

